title: iTools Pro 4.3.9.5 for Windows / 1.7.9.8 macOS !{Latest}
description:
iTools Pro 4.3.9.5 for Windows / 1.7.9.8 macOS !{Latest}

iTools is the best analog of the official Apple iTunes application, which even bypasses the opponent in some moments. The utility was created in China and, unlike the Apple version, it has a number of advantages.

The program has a wide functionality, performs its functions faster and has a number of other advantages.


Key features:
• Transfer audio / video / photo between PC and iOS and back.
• Instant photo export from your mobile device.
• Ability to create ringtones.
• Back up or restore data on Apple devices.
• Connect to PC using both cable and Wi-Fi.
• The presence of the icon manager, through which you can sort icons on your device, as well as perform backup / restore location.
• The battery master, with which you can find out detailed information about the battery of your device (real capacity, design capacity, boot voltage, serial number of the battery, etc.) and its condition.
• Full support with iPhone 8/8 Plus and iOS 11.

iTools Icon Arranger
The iTools icon arranger helps you to manage icons on your iPhone, iPad or iPod screen. If there are hundreds of icons on your screen, you can manage them through your PCs' wide screen. If you need you can remove any icon from the screen with this icon manager tool.

OS: Windows 10, Windows 8 / 8.1, Windows 7, Vista
